  "universal_guidelines": [
    "NEVER use generic gradients. Use noise textures + radial gradients for depth.",
    "Text hierarchy: Headings must be uppercase and tracked tight. Body text relaxed.",
    "Inputs and Forms: Use 'fluted glass' effect - semi-transparent with blur.",
    "Images: Always add a subtle vignette to blend them into the dark background.",
    "Buttons: Avoid default rounded-md. Use full pill shapes (rounded-full) or sharp edges (rounded-none) for 'Ticket' feel.",
    "Use 'sonner' for toasts.",
    "All interactive elements must have data-testid."
  ],
  "instructions_to_main_agent": "Refactor the existing frontend to match this Crystal/Luxury aesthetic. Start by installing the new fonts (Tenor Sans, Manrope, Unbounded). Replace the standard Tailwind colors with the new palette in tailwind.config.js. Update the global CSS for base styles. Then, rewrite the main layout and homepage components to use the glassmorphism and bento grid strategies. Ensure the 'Raffle' page feels distinctively 'Golden' and premium."
